cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper introduces a multi-vehicle trajectory generator using machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also involves computer vision techniques for data processing and analysis (cs.CV). The application of the proposed method is in the field of robotics and autonomous vehicles (cs.RO, cs.SY).
